summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of 10th Avenue Northeast from Sylvester Place to East 65th street, et al. in the City of Seattle by laying watermains, etc. under Ordinance No. 21615 creating Local Improvement District No. 2156 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
